{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"56888ef3cc","title":"畅所欲言(小喜剧)","origin":"《重庆市右派言论选辑第五集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共重庆市委宣传部办公室编印，1957年9月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"02f038a954","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":5,"articleId":"56888ef3cc"}],"tags":[{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3d6e05a0be","name":"重庆"},{"id":"6e0d691660","name":"石曼"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b65f2698f4","type":"title","text":"畅所欲言(小喜剧)","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"134a4dc2e8","type":"authors","text":"重庆石曼","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"288824b77a","type":"paragraph","text":"[编者按：石曼，出身于商人之家。现为重庆市文工团文学创作组组长，解放前曾被特务逮捕写了悔过书。1950年入党，因隐瞒历史而被取消候补资格。在鸣放中，石曼与右派分子董时光相互勾结，狼狈为奸。在市文工团煽动群众到市委请愿，上大街贴标语，并伸言要：“叫他们(指党员)一败涂地”。石曼在这个小剧中，以极端仇视党的感情来丑化党的领导干部，污蔑领导干部压制民主，惧怕鸣放。并巧妙地借“部长”的嘴，道出作者要搞大民主，要踢开党的领导的阴险企图。]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"6aa15b1be0","type":"paragraph","text":"甲上，手执上联示观众，念：“百花齐放万紫千红”，贴右面。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"38395cfc51","type":"paragraph","text":"乙上，手执下联示观众，念：“百家争鸣语惊山河”，贴左面。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"8d9aa57026","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任上，执横额示观众，念：“畅所欲言”，爬到凳子上贴得高高的。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"9bf8ce0437","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(和甲，乙见礼毕)同志们，开会了。(清嗓子，宣叙式地)为了正确地处理人民内部矛盾，今天，扩大我们的民主生活。大家可以根据“百花齐放，百家争鸣”的精神，畅所欲言。尽量地提意见，多多地提意见。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"957ce98a3d","type":"paragraph","text":"(甲、乙互视，不信任，沉默。)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"fbbae12464","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：我们这个单位，以往民主生活开展的不够。不过，基本上应该说是好的。但是，不够也是肯定的。现在，我要大大地放手。大家大胆地“放”，大胆地“鸣”。那位同志先来。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"d43c760fd7","type":"paragraph","text":"(甲、乙无反应。)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"4e312c1ed8","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：甲同志，你年轻气盛，开头炮，先“鸣”一“鸣”。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"f4a4ebc041","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：啊！我？","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"378c4e0987","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：对，就是你。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"cc3c965b46","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：我。唉！不“鸣”算了。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"f12e0491ac","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：不“鸣”不行，这是上级的号召。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"437060823b","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：我能不能不“鸣”？","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"5b87936712","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：不能不“鸣”。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"11699d0b4c","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：一定要“鸣”？","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"02f0cf9840","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：一定要“鸣”。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"3b38b9968a","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：(鼓足勇气)那我就大胆地“鸣”一声，“鸣”的不对，请高主任批判。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"a71a147763","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(鼓掌)欢迎，欢迎。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"44248e1eb1","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：去年我到办公室请假，撕了办公桌上半张公家信纸写假条，(向高)有这回事吧？","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"393d33d0e0","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：有这回事，是我亲眼瞅见的。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"ba80adb8d9","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：高主任说我用国家财产办私人的事，提高到原则上来看是贪污行为；从发展上来看，将来要变成刘青山、张子善，走上反党、反人民的道路。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"2318452035","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：分析的很正确。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"56818b26ec","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：正确？我想……","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"a21cf599ff","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：你想什么？","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"d5775b0d88","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：我想现在是不是可以重新研究一下。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"703e77749c","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：你想翻案？这问题去年年终鉴定已经作了结论，作过结论的问题这里不谈。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"51bcf90896","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：不谈！好吧。(欲下。)","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"d5777d3995","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：怎么，你没有啦？","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"4303150b97","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：没有谈的啦。(下。)","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"843fc92892","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(向台下)好，请大家注意，要打破顾虑、“畅所欲言”。乙同志来吧，乙同志素来是“不鸣则已，一鸣惊人”的。今天一定有宝贵意见。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"84de3adb7a","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：我有三不通。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"7475a1bbec","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：三不通！你精简一下。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"e98cbded5f","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：精简过啦，不精简就有三十不通，三百不通了。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"f0e1093e3c","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(吃惊)啊！好，我们是“畅所欲言”，还是说你的“三不通”吧。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"7648abfba5","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：第一不通，高主任私心太重。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"6dd9f2ab6d","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：你说我？","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"fa20b6a3e0","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：我的孩子要进托儿所，申请了两年，主任说没有办法。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"92ed76fcb8","type":"subtitle","text":"高主任：一点办法都没有。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"945b84bb09","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：高主任的孩子，前天刚从家乡接来，昨天就进了托儿所。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"826a463e3e","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：这个……","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"fe6ff9cb92","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：连不是我们单位的、主任的外甥、外甥女，主任也都把他们送进去了。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"3a00a9090c","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：这是特殊情况，闹不得平均主义。我那个妹夫是老干部……","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"fb3a5f01a9","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：多会儿参军的。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"b0bd94a167","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：嗯，……1950年参军的。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"a2cdc0d832","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：1950年参军的老干部。","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"e03558311f","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：老干部的子女应该照顾照顾。平均主义这个东西可不是无产阶级思想，它是……","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"69369c2381","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：(一字一字地)它是小资产阶级思想的产物。我知道。你甭说了，我啥意见也没有了。(下。)","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"2139d584a7","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：没意见就好了，我们是“畅所欲言”。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"4c67788200","type":"paragraph","text":"(老先生兴奋地上。)","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"2ccf4a9634","type":"paragraph","text":"老先生：毛主席的报告令我钦佩，令我振奋，真是“东风到处百花开”，我……","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"13c5e96c55","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：老先生来的正好，请坐，今天我们是(指对联)……老先生：(念)“百花齐放万紫千红，百家争鸣语惊山河”，壮哉，壮哉！","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"fa617e3dd1","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：老先生，还有，(指横额)“畅所欲言”。","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"969940cd22","type":"paragraph","text":"老先生：“畅所欲言”，一定、一定。高主任，有一个意见在我肚子里放了五年了。","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"9c97f0166e","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(旁白)老先生是慎重行事的人，不象那两个年轻的乱放大炮。(转过身来)老先生请说。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"7d9c0d1860","type":"paragraph","text":"老先生：汉字有世界各国文字所没有的优点，我反对文字改革。","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"48b801675a","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：慢点，慢点，你反对什么？","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"0554eef466","type":"paragraph","text":"老先生：反对文字改革。","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"817b8e4129","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(旁白)不象话了。","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"b6cd64164b","type":"paragraph","text":"老先生：照你说，意见提不得罗。","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"2b55e131be","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：这也请老先生自己考虑。我是提倡“畅所欲言”，不怕天下大乱的。","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"21858e014d","type":"paragraph","text":"老先生：既然提不得，人民日报上怎又提得呢？","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"b0d50d5ec0","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：啊！人民日报反对文字改革？几号的报纸，快找来看看。(转着找报纸)那您的意见当然就提得，我不是说了吗，我本来就提倡“畅所欲言”的。","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"c0900ad741","type":"paragraph","text":"老先生：(气咻咻，一字一字地)不是人民日报反对文字改革，是有人在人民日报上反对文字改革。","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"94ed6b91d2","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(闻声站住)哦，(不找报了)那情况就不一样了，慎重地考虑考虑吧。我们自己要有独立的见解，不要见风使舵，作人家尾巴。","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"95086258a6","type":"paragraph","text":"老先生：现在有些年轻人不孝顺父母，不敬师长，我很气愤。我建议政府提倡中国的传统道德，忠、孝、仁、爱、信、义、和、平。","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"b397be3050","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(旁白)天下非大乱不可了。(转过身来)忠、孝、仁、爱、信、义、和、平，这是谁的思想？是孔子？不是，不是。是孟子？也不是。是老子？不，都不是。(搞不清了)总归是封建道德。(忽有所悟似的)嗯，你反对文字改革，这是一方面，你提倡忠、孝、仁、爱……这又是一方面；两方面联系起来看，你是要我们放弃社会主义建设成果，回到封建社会去。你居心何在？","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"a1f76be855","type":"paragraph","text":"老先生：(惊，擦汗)啊！(部长同甲、乙上。)","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"5c2888f53e","type":"paragraph","text":"部长：谁在说话，口气挺吓唬人的。","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"187bf49177","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：不，我在贯彻上级指示，扩大民主生活，叫大家“畅所欲言”。","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"81e2cdffbe","type":"paragraph","text":"部长：好，我听听，那位同志先放一把火。","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"379415fc5d","type":"paragraph","text":"(众沉默。甲抽烟，乙挖手指，老先生擦眼镜。)","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"95d4b50c3f","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：你们，大家说话啊。(众沉默如故。)","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"f1cb5c231c","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(对部长)大家基本上……都拥护毛主席的报告。","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"7618138617","type":"paragraph","text":"甲乙：(同时的)不是基本上，是从心眼里百分之百的拥护。","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"e67a8fe937","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：对，百分之百的拥护。刚才大家已经“畅所欲言”，言无不尽。","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"e422695722","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：报告部长，不是言无不尽，是言没有尽。我才谈了一个问题，高主任就制止了我发言。","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"3748cbaf10","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(旁白)这个该死的，无组织无纪律，今年年终鉴定还要给他记上一条。","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"427d652699","type":"paragraph","text":"部长：喂，你在哪里叽咕什么？","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"42738f1945","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：我，我说甲同志工作积极，应该给他加薪。","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"2531d1140b","type":"paragraph","text":"部长：乙同志，你说？","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"c96d1320b9","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：我有罪，不敢发言。","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"df8fe54b98","type":"paragraph","text":"部长：恕你无罪。","index":84,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"6df7df0e79","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：刚才我挖了高主任的老根，我说他私心太重，高主任封给我一个平均主义。","index":85,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"7859aa54ab","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(旁白)这个混蛋，他孩子入托儿所的问题，再隔80年也不给他解决。","index":86,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"56ca1a9050","type":"paragraph","text":"部长：你又在哪里叽咕什么？","index":87,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"b465210e3e","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：我，我说乙同志能“畅所欲言”，应该给他表扬。","index":88,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"42767eb8cb","type":"paragraph","text":"部长：老先生，您发表点意见。","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"ca9f48dcbb","type":"paragraph","text":"老先生：我这会儿喘不过气来。","index":90,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"23cb583534","type":"paragraph","text":"部长：为什么？身体欠安。","index":91,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"709ca5ee46","type":"paragraph","text":"老先生：有顶帽子压住，一顶封建主义的大帽子刚才压在我头上。","index":92,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"15b13fc37f","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(旁白)这个老混蛋，今年到北戴河去休养，算没他的份了。","index":93,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"411dc35668","type":"paragraph","text":"部长：是谁替你扣上的帽子，还叫谁替你取下来。","index":94,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"30d3322e38","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(赶紧地)来了，来了。(施礼)老先生，刚才我的话算没说。","index":95,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"23f6e9384c","type":"paragraph","text":"部长：(对大家)以后再发生这样的事，你们就告他妨碍言论自由。小民主都没有的话，就给他来个大民主。","index":96,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"253fad31e2","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(慌忙地)可别来大民主，我保证今后让大家(指横额)畅…畅…畅…(一阵风吹来，把“畅所欲言”横额刮跑了。主任大惊。)啊！(赶紧追上拾起。)","index":97,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"64bb92289b","type":"paragraph","text":"部长：你看看，风都对你的“畅所欲言”有意见。","index":98,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"fccd75446f","type":"paragraph","text":"(高主任站在凳子上去贴横额。)","index":99,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"946f012ee9","type":"paragraph","text":"部长：同志们，火我已经替你们放了，你们有意见“大胆地‘放’，大胆地‘鸣’”吧。","index":100,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"681f13679c","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：从小到大，我说。(掏出一张发言提纲来。)","index":101,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"1637ac3ed6","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：(抢先的)我说，我说。(掏出几张发言提纲来。)","index":102,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"3b6deac222","type":"paragraph","text":"老先生：先老后少，待老夫奏上几本。(掏出一大迭意见书来。)","index":103,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"35d69b9200","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(在高凳上，大惊)天啦！这么多意见，有好几百条，他们这是存心塌我台来的。","index":104,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"5d5c977b14","type":"paragraph","text":"部长：你在说什么？","index":105,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"dff57d7d83","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：我说……这一大堆意见，要是传到台湾去，没好处，有坏处。我们领导要掌握一下。","index":106,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"1204dcc179","type":"paragraph","text":"部长：还没“放”，就先掌握。你既不赞成“放”，又不愿意改，那就不必为难了。你把主任的工作交代一下，休息去吧。","index":107,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"3a3fc8c194","type":"paragraph","text":"高主任：(如雷击身)啊！(自凳子上跌下)我赞成“放”，大民主也行。主任……我可要当。","index":108,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"c326fafa4e","type":"paragraph","text":"——幕闭——","index":109,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"},{"id":"db71435168","type":"paragraph","text":" (原载重庆日报6月5日)","index":110,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc"}],"page":{"id":"c58a786072","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56888ef3cc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}